    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it's ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available now is this driver-focused mid-engine coupe, powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This example boasts a 6-speed manual transmission with short-throw linkage, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a low polar moment of inertia and a well-sorted suspension geometry that ensures neutral handling characteristics. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent high-pressure fuel pump replacement and a brake system service featuring four-piston monobloc calipers. While showing minor cosmetic patina on the leading edges consistent with regular use, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a visceral analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Reliable performance. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly balances luxury with daily reliability. The exterior is finished in a Deep Charcoal Metallic that still retains a brilliant shine from regular detailing; while you might find a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with highway use, the body is remarkably straight and free of dings. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features premium black leather upholstery that has been treated regularly to prevent cracking, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster. All technological features, including the responsive touchscreen navigation, dual-zone climate control, and the power-sliding sunroof, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, using only full-synthetic oil every 5,000 miles. Most recently, the vehicle received new brake pads and a fresh set of all-season tires with approximately 80% tread remaining. This car comes with a clean title, a full set of floor mats, two key fobs, and a complete folder of service records. It is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive excellence, maintained to a high standard of mechanical and aesthetic integrity. This vehicle offers a superior driving experience, characterized by its consistent performance and refined interior appointments. Every system has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for reliability and roadworthiness. We invite serious inquiries for this exceptional offering, which represents a prudent investment in both luxury and long-term utility.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
