      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. Honestly, I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014very well-cared for and runs like a total dream. It's the perfect match for someone who wants a reliable, stylish ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m more than happy to chat, answer any questions, or have you come by for a test drive whenever works for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29900.0,
