    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and eight individual throttle bodies. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission, sending power through a variable M differential lock. The chassis maintains its composure with precise M-tuned suspension and a hydraulic steering rack that provides unfiltered feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and throttle valve actuator service, ensuring the double-VANOS system operates with peak timing accuracy. A mechanically sound example that delivers a visceral, high-induction-note driving experience.",
